msgid "## Deployment"
msgstr "## 部署"

msgid "### Troubleshooting"
msgstr "### 故障排除"

msgid "Run into"
msgstr "遇到"

msgid ""
"\"openai_harmony.HarmonyError: error downloading or loading vocab file: "
"failed to download or load vocab error\""
msgstr ""
"\"openai_harmony.HarmonyError: error downloading or loading vocab file: "
"failed to download or load vocab error\""

msgid ""
"Solution: This is caused by a bug in openai_harmony code. This can be worked"
" around by downloading the tiktoken encoding files in advance and setting "
"the TIKTOKEN_ENCODINGS_BASE environment variable. See this "
"[GitHub](https://github.com/openai/harmony/pull/41) issue for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"解决方案：这是由 openai_harmony 代码中的错误引起的。可以通过提前下载 tiktoken 编码文件并设置 "
"TIKTOKEN_ENCODINGS_BASE 环境变量来解决。有关更多信息，请参阅此 "
"[GitHub](https://github.com/openai/harmony/pull/41) 问题。"

